text: Nico & Vinz are a Norwegian pop duo from Oslo. The current members are Kahouly Nicolay "Nico" Sereba and Vincent "Vinz" Dery. They formed in 2010 as Envy but changed their name to Nico & Vinz by the end of 2012. Their biggest hit single was "Am I Wrong", released in 2013. It went to number 2 in Norway, Denmark and Sweden, number 1 in the United Kingdom and number 4 in the United States. == Related pages == * Ylvis * Pvris Category:Boy bands Category:2010 establishments in Europe Category:21st-century establishments in Norway Category:Musical groups from Oslo Category:Pop music groups
